---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import CallToAction from "../../components/CallToAction.astro";
import ServiceFooter from "../../components/ServiceFooter.astro";
---

<Layout title="Bathroom Remodeling in Seattle | S&S Construction">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="absolute -top-80 left-[max(6rem,33%)] -z-10 transform-gpu blur-3xl sm:left-1/2 md:top-20 lg:ml-20 xl:top-3 xl:ml-56"
    >
      <div
        style="clip-path: polygon(63.1% 29.6%, 100% 17.2%, 76.7% 3.1%, 48.4% 0.1%, 44.6% 4.8%, 54.5% 25.4%, 59.8% 49.1%, 55.3% 57.9%, 44.5% 57.3%, 27.8% 48%, 35.1% 81.6%, 0% 97.8%, 39.3% 100%, 35.3% 81.5%, 97.2% 52.8%, 63.1% 29.6%)"
        class="aspect-801/1036 w-200.25 bg-linear-to-tr from-[#ff80b5] to-[#9089fc] opacity-30"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl mb-36 px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
        <p class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-indigo-600">
          For homes and condos across Seattle — from functional updates to full
          renovations.
        </p>
        <h1
          class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl"
        >
          High-quality bathroom remodel
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl/8 text-gray-700">
          If your bathroom feels outdated, cramped, or poorly laid out, a
          remodel can dramatically improve comfort, function, and resale value.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:mt-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-12"
      >
        <div class="relative lg:order-last lg:col-span-5">
          <svg
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="absolute -top-160 left-1 -z-10 h-256 w-702 -translate-x-1/2 mask-[radial-gradient(64rem_64rem_at_111.5rem_0%,white,transparent)] stroke-gray-900/10"
          >
            <defs>
              <pattern
                id="e87443c8-56e4-4c20-9111-55b82fa704e3"
                width="200"
                height="200"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
              >
                <path d="M0.5 0V200M200 0.5L0 0.499983"></path>
              </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect
              width="100%"
              height="100%"
              fill="url(#e87443c8-56e4-4c20-9111-55b82fa704e3)"
              stroke-width="0"></rect>
          </svg>
          <figure class="border-l border-indigo-600 pl-8">
            <blockquote
              class="text-xl/8 font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900"
            >
              <p>
                "They remodeled our condo bathroom in Belltown and handled it
                professionally from start to finish. Communication was excellent
                and the workmanship was top-notch."
              </p>
            </blockquote>
            <figcaption class="mt-8 flex gap-x-4">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502685104226-ee32379fefbe?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=facearea&facepad=2&w=256&h=256&q=80"
                alt=""
                class="mt-1 size-10 flex-none rounded-full bg-gray-50"
              />
              <div class="text-sm/6">
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Roman Turner</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600">Belltown Seattle</div>
              </div>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-xl text-base/7 text-gray-600 lg:col-span-7">
          <p>
            We specialize in small to mid-size bathroom remodels throughout
            Seattle, including condos, townhomes, and older homes that require
            careful planning and clean execution. We handle the entire process —
            design coordination, permits, construction, and final walkthrough —
            so you get a smooth experience and a bathroom that lasts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <CallToAction />

    <!-- Bento Grid -->
    <div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-indigo-600">Featured</h2>
        <p
          class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-950 sm:text-5xl"
        >
          Previous Bathroom Remodel Projects
        </p>
        <div
          class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:mt-16 lg:grid-cols-6 lg:grid-rows-2"
        >
          <div class="relative lg:col-span-3">
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-white max-lg:rounded-t-4xl lg:rounded-tl-4xl"
            >
            </div>
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div
              class="relative flex h-full flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[calc(var(--radius-lg)+1px)] max-lg:rounded-t-[calc(2rem+1px)] lg:rounded-tl-[calc(2rem+1px)]"
            >
              <img
                src="/images/bathroom/queen-anne-bath-1.jpg"
                alt=""
                class="h-80 object-cover object-left"
              />
              <div class="p-10 pt-4">
                <h3 class="text-sm/4 font-semibold text-indigo-600">
                  Ballard condo bathroom remodel
                </h3>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950"
                >
                  Outdated tub replaced with a full tile shower
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
                  This condo bathroom felt dark and cramped, with aging fixtures
                  and poor waterproofing. We rebuilt the shower with modern
                  tile, improved lighting, and a clean vanity layout that
                  maximized space without changing the footprint.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div
              class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm outline outline-black/5 max-lg:rounded-t-4xl lg:rounded-tl-4xl"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative lg:col-span-3">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-white lg:rounded-tr-4xl">
            </div>
            <div
              class="relative flex h-full flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[calc(var(--radius-lg)+1px)] lg:rounded-tr-[calc(2rem+1px)]"
            >
              <img
                src="/images/bathroom/bellevue-bath-1.jpg"
                alt=""
                class="h-80 object-cover object-left lg:object-right"
              />
              <div class="p-10 pt-4">
                <h3 class="text-sm/4 font-semibold text-indigo-600">
                  Queen Anne home bathroom remodel
                </h3>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950"
                >
                  Small bathroom, smarter layout
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
                  An older home bathroom with limited space and awkward
                  clearances needed a functional upgrade. We reworked the
                  layout, installed durable finishes, and delivered a brighter,
                  more usable bathroom while keeping the original character
                  intact.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm outline outline-black/5 lg:rounded-tr-4xl"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative lg:col-span-2">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-white lg:rounded-bl-4xl">
            </div>
            <div
              class="relative flex h-full flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[calc(var(--radius-lg)+1px)] lg:rounded-bl-[calc(2rem+1px)]"
            >
              <img
                src="/images/bathroom/w-seattle-bath-1.jpg"
                alt=""
                class="h-80 object-cover object-left"
              />
              <div class="p-10 pt-4">
                <h3 class="text-sm/4 font-semibold text-indigo-600">
                  Capitol Hill condo bathroom renovation
                </h3>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950"
                >
                  HOA-approved condo remodel with modern finishes
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
                  This project required coordination with building rules and
                  restricted work hours. We handled approvals, upgraded the
                  shower and flooring, and completed the remodel cleanly and
                  efficiently with minimal disruption to the building.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm outline outline-black/5 lg:rounded-bl-4xl"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative lg:col-span-2">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-white"></div>
            <div
              class="relative flex h-full flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[calc(var(--radius-lg)+1px)]"
            >
              <img
                src="/images/bathroom/pinehurst-bath-1.jpg"
                alt=""
                class="h-80 object-cover"
              />
              <div class="p-10 pt-4">
                <h3 class="text-sm/4 font-semibold text-indigo-600">
                  Green Lake primary bathroom remodel
                </h3>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950"
                >
                  From dated and worn to clean and modern
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
                  The original bathroom showed signs of water damage and aging
                  materials. We rebuilt the space with proper waterproofing, new
                  tile, and updated fixtures for a long-lasting, low-maintenance
                  finish.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm outline outline-black/5"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative lg:col-span-2">
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 rounded-lg bg-white max-lg:rounded-b-4xl lg:rounded-br-4xl"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="relative flex h-full flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[calc(var(--radius-lg)+1px)] max-lg:rounded-b-[calc(2rem+1px)] lg:rounded-br-[calc(2rem+1px)]"
            >
              <img
                src="/images/bathroom/ravenna-bath-3.jpg"
                alt=""
                class="h-80 object-cover"
              />
              <div class="p-10 pt-4">
                <h3 class="text-sm/4 font-semibold text-indigo-600">
                  West Seattle bathroom remodel
                </h3>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950"
                >
                  Functional upgrade for a busy household
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
                  This bathroom needed to handle daily use without constant
                  maintenance issues. We focused on durable materials, improved
                  ventilation, and a layout that balances style with everyday
                  practicality.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-lg shadow-sm outline outline-black/5 max-lg:rounded-b-4xl lg:rounded-br-4xl"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Service List -->
  <div class="bg-white pb-16 sm:pb-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div
        class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-5"
      >
        <div class="col-span-2">
          <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-indigo-600">
            Bathroom Remodeling Services We Offer
          </h2>
          <p
            class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl"
          >
            Services we've done for other homes and condos across Seattle
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-base/7 text-gray-700">
            — from functional updates to full renovations.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10 pt-6 flex items-center gap-x-6 lg:mt-0 lg:shrink-0">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-xs hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600"
            >
              Free Estimate
            </a>
            <a href="/services" class="text-sm/6 font-semibold text-gray-900">
              More Services
              <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <dl
          class="col-span-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 text-base/7 text-gray-600 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16"
        >
          <div class="relative pl-9">
            <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                data-slot="icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="absolute top-1 left-0 size-5 text-indigo-500"
              >
                <path
                  d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                  fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Full bathroom remodels
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              Complete tear-outs and rebuilds that update layout, finishes, and
              functionality from top to bottom.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-9">
            <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                data-slot="icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="absolute top-1 left-0 size-5 text-indigo-500"
              >
                <path
                  d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                  fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Small bathroom renovations
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              Smart upgrades designed to make compact bathrooms feel more open,
              efficient, and comfortable.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-9">
            <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                data-slot="icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="absolute top-1 left-0 size-5 text-indigo-500"
              >
                <path
                  d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                  fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Condo and apartment bathrooms
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              Bathroom remodels coordinated with HOA rules, building access, and
              approved work hours.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-9">
            <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                data-slot="icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="absolute top-1 left-0 size-5 text-indigo-500"
              >
                <path
                  d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                  fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Shower remodels & walk-in showers
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              Custom showers built with proper waterproofing, modern tile, and
              clean, accessible designs.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-9">
            <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                data-slot="icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="absolute top-1 left-0 size-5 text-indigo-500"
              >
                <path
                  d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                  fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Tub replacements & conversions
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              Replace worn tubs or convert to showers to improve usability and
              modernize the space.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-9">
            <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                data-slot="icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="absolute top-1 left-0 size-5 text-indigo-500"
              >
                <path
                  d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                  fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Tile flooring & shower surrounds
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              Durable, professionally installed tile that looks great and stands
              up to daily use.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-9">
            <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                data-slot="icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="absolute top-1 left-0 size-5 text-indigo-500"
              >
                <path
                  d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                  fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Vanities, lighting, and ventilation upgrades
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              Updated fixtures and airflow improvements that enhance comfort,
              visibility, and moisture control.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-9">
            <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
              <svg
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                data-slot="icon"
                aria-hidden="true"
                class="absolute top-1 left-0 size-5 text-indigo-500"
              >
                <path
                  d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                  fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Waterproofing and code-compliant installations
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              Every bathroom is built to meet current codes with proper
              waterproofing behind the finishes.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ServiceFooter />
</Layout>
